steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab list with name "Pages"
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT004Screen
Then I should see the screen with name JIT004Screen display in list Pages
When I add new screen with name testingDuplicate
Then I should see the screen with name testingDuplicate display in list Pages
When I duplicate screen with name JIT004Screen to invalid<>@#?!_duplicateJIT004Screen
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Special characters are not allowed"
When I close the modal popup
When I duplicate screen with name JIT004Screen to empty
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Name is required"
When I close the modal popup
When I duplicate screen with name JIT004Screen to JIT004Screen
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Name has been taken, Please use another one"
When I close the modal popup
When I duplicate screen with name JIT004Screen to duplicateJIT004Screen
Then I should see the screen with name duplicateJIT004Screen display in list Pages
When I duplicate screen with name testingDuplicate to DEFAULT
Then I should see the screen with name testingDuplicateCopy1 display in list Pages
When I duplicate screen with name duplicateJIT004Screen to DEFAULT
Then I should see the screen with name duplicateJIT004ScreenCopy1 display in list Pages
When I add new screen with name testingContentJIT004Screen
When I select screen with name testingContentJIT004Screen
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "testingContentJIT004Screen" with index "1"
When I add item "View" in Search popup to preview mobile editor
Then I should see the preview mobile editor match with image title "JIT008.Search.Components.View"
